        <mxCell id="p4-flow-box" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF3E0;strokeColor=#FF6D00;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontColor=#E65100;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Approval Gate Flow:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Agent wants to use high-risk tool (e.g., delete files)&lt;br&gt;2. &lt;code&gt;can_use_tool&lt;/code&gt; callback fires in ClaudeSDKClient&lt;br&gt;3. Writes approval request to DynamoDB&lt;br&gt;4. Task -&gt; AWAITING_APPROVAL&lt;br&gt;5. WebSocket notifies user with tool details&lt;br&gt;6. User approves/denies via WebSocket or CLI&lt;br&gt;7. Callback returns PermissionResultAllow/Deny&lt;br&gt;8. Task -&gt; RUNNING (continues or receives denial)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Timeout:&lt;/b&gt; 5 min (auto-deny)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Scope:&lt;/b&gt; Per tool call (not blanket)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="250" width="380" x="100" y="520" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="q_GZwcvPX2EDaeb1fLDq-1" edge="1" parent="1" source="p4-awaiting" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;strokeColor=#C62828;dashed=1;exitX=0.999;exitY=0.528;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=-0.007;entryY=0.598;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;exitPerimeter=0;entryPerimeter=0;" target="p4-timedout">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
